Class RFParams

java.lang.Object
  org.life.sl.routefinder.RFParams

public class RFParams
extends java.lang.Object

Container for the configuration parameters of the routefinding algorithm; includes methods for reading the parameters from an ini-file.

Author:
Bernhard Barkow
See Also:
